NEW Hover to zoom Color Select Guitar Color Black Blue Sparkle Fingerboard Material Select Guitar Color Rosewood $2,249.00 Notify Me When Available Find A Dealer Made in Japan Limited Super-Sonic™ $2,249.00 Made in Japan Limited Super-Sonic ™ is based on the Super-Sonic ™, which was launched under the Squier brand in the late 1990s as the Squier Vista Series and then reprinted in Mexico as the Pawn Shop Series in 2012. In addition, it is a limited edition product that more faithfully reproduces the looks of the Squier Vista Serie at that time with the high quality of Made in Japan. In addition to the impactful looks with a reverse head and two humbuckers on the reverse body shape, the controls are also characteristic of Volume 1. (Bridge Pickup) and Volume 2. (Neck Pickup). Basswood body with "U" shaped maple neck, 9.5 inch radius rosewood fingerboard and medium jumbo frets for smooth playability, Dragster BB pickups and Vintage-Style Synchronized Tremolo bridge for playability. And bring a range to the sound.
